&quot;Heap Big Chief getting acquainted with fire stick of paleface. Group of Indians, on a visit to the &quot;U. S. S. Recruit&quot; in New York to aid in recruiting, examining the machine gun aboard that &quot;vessel.&quot; Chief Bald Eagle, leader of the band, is aiming the weapon.&quot;

