The Sunday Oregonian, August 12, 1917, SECTION FIVE, Image 67 printed this photo with the caption:
&quot;One of the big figures which has grown out of this war is that of General J. C. Smuts, once a Boer commander and enemy of Great Britain. He is now a member of the Imperial Council, working in co-operation with I the government in prosecuting the war.&quot;
<a href="http://oregonnews.uoregon.edu/lccn/sn83045782/1917-08-12/ed-1/seq-67/" rel="nofollow">oregonnews.uoregon.edu/lccn/sn83045782/1917-08-12/ed-1/se...</a>

